-throwing-torch-at-cop/0000018f-3551-d516-afbf-ffd31e110000</guid></item><item><title>AG：以色列政府将正统草案视为继续司法改革以逃避实施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/ag-state-treats-haredi-draft-as-continuation-of-judicial-overhaul-to-evade-implementation/0000018f-35a5-d8fb-a1df-bde79d720000</link><description>政府正试图绕过向高等法院请愿书中对单独律师的有限许可，并将其应用于所有部委</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 19:45:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/ag-state-treats-haredi-draft-as-continuation-of-judicial-overhaul-to-evade-implementation/0000018f-35a5-d8fb-a1df-bde79d720000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚总统佩特罗表示将因加沙战争与以色列断绝外交关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/colombian-president-petro-says-will-break-diplomatic-relations-with-israel/0000018f-357f-d9c3-abcf-7f7f680b0000</link><description>以色列外交部长在回应这一消息时称总统为“反犹太主义者”；哥伦比亚消息人士称，哥伦比亚外交部长和其他政府高级官员没有收到总统决定的通知</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 18:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/colombian-president-petro-says-will-break-diplomatic-relations-with-israel/0000018f-357f-d9c3-abcf-7f7f680b0000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚的特权占屋者和曼哈顿版本的空投援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-01/ty-article/.highlight/columbias-entitled-squatters-and-the-manhattan-version-of-air-dropped-aid/0000018f-353b-d8fb-a1df-bd7fd4420000</link><description>值得指出的是，警方不仅为汉密尔顿大厅的人们提供了随时自愿离开的机会，而且在抗议者遭受苦难的十二个小时中，哥伦比亚大学校园内随时提供食物、水和厕所</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 18:46:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-01/ty-article/.highlight/columbias-entitled-squatters-and-the-manhattan-version-of-air-dropped-aid/0000018f-353b-d8fb-a1df-bd7fd4420000</guid></item><item><title>“对于一些犹太人来说，围绕加沙的校园战争很糟糕。但它们并不是暴力、反犹太主义的噩梦”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-01/ty-article-podcast/for-jews-campus-wars-over-gaza-suck-but-theyre-not-a-violent-antisemitic-nightmare/0000018f-34c2-d0b5-a59f-35c7d90d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 18:42:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-01/ty-article-podcast/for-jews-campus-wars-over-gaza-suck-but-theyre-not-a-violent-antisemitic-nightmare/0000018f-34c2-d0b5-a59f-35c7d90d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 208 天：布林肯表示拉法行动将减少人质交易的机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-208-blinken-says-rafah-op-will-diminish-chances-of-hostage-deal/0000018f-3500-d444-ab9f-f50f5a690001</link><description>布林肯在以色列会见内塔尼亚胡总理，称哈马斯是停火/人质释放协议无法达成的唯一原因 ■ 以色列代表团抵达开罗继续停火谈判 ■ 据报道，埃及停火提案的措辞不包括以色列的承诺不要返回加沙 ■ 约旦官方媒体报道，以色列定居者袭击了两支前往加沙的援助车队 ■ 战争进入 208 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-208-blinken-says-rafah-op-will-diminish-chances-of-hostage-deal/0000018f-3500-d444-ab9f-f50f5a690001</guid></item><item><title>美国联合航空表示 5 月 9 日前飞往特拉维夫的航班已取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/united-airlines-says-flights-to-tel-aviv-are-cancelled-up-to-may-9/0000018f-3492-d8c4-afef-3dfe63ed0000</link><description>由于以色列和伊朗袭击事件后的安全担忧，该航空公司取消了 5 月 2 日之前飞往以色列的航班，并已将航班延期一周，以完成安全评估</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 15:22:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/united-airlines-says-flights-to-tel-aviv-are-cancelled-up-to-may-9/0000018f-3492-d8c4-afef-3dfe63ed0000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列与哈马斯协议的乐观情绪减弱，针对拉法的行动可能会导致人质丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/optimism-wanes-over-israel-hamas-deal-and-a-move-on-rafah-could-cost-hostages-lives/0000018f-33f3-d9c3-abcf-7bf7d07e0000</link><description>尽管调解人担心哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔会拒绝埃及的提议，但以色列极右翼部长们却力图阻止任何协议。 ■ 尽管国际社会反对，行动上也遇到困难，内塔尼亚胡仍坚持主张拉法入侵，冒着人质、士兵和平民遭受损失的风险</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 15:13:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/optimism-wanes-over-israel-hamas-deal-and-a-move-on-rafah-could-cost-hostages-lives/0000018f-33f3-d9c3-abcf-7bf7d07e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队削减守卫约旦河西岸定居点的士兵人数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-slashes-number-of-soldiers-guarding-west-bank-settlements/0000018f-3455-dbd5-a7df-fef7a7350000</link><description>战争爆发后，戒备状态下的士兵人数达到8000人，随后逐渐减少，目前只剩下1000人。这一削减是与定居点协调进行的，允许更多的定居者携带武器</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-slashes-number-of-soldiers-guarding-west-bank-settlements/0000018f-3455-dbd5-a7df-fef7a7350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院驳回被监禁的巴勒斯坦人巴尔古提对监禁条款的上诉，援引哈马斯合作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-rejects-barghouti-appeal-on-imprisonment-terms-cites-hamas-collaboration/0000018f-3438-d9c3-abcf-7e7d34760000</link><description>过去几个月一直被单独监禁的法塔赫高级官员声称，他没有获得基本设备。法院表示，Marwan Barghouti 的请愿书忽略了自 10 月 7 日以来安全囚犯条款的变化</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-rejects-barghouti-appeal-on-imprisonment-terms-cites-hamas-collaboration/0000018f-3438-d9c3-abcf-7e7d34760000</guid></item><item><title>美国终于找到了对以色列和内塔尼亚胡的有效影响力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/america-has-finally-found-effective-leverage-on-israel-and-netanyahu/0000018f-339c-d8fb-a1df-bffe7d110000</link><description>即使国际刑事法院检察官卡里姆·汗尚未对本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和其他以色列高级官员发出逮捕令，其影响也已经在加沙和人质谈判中显现出来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:18:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/america-has-finally-found-effective-leverage-on-israel-and-netanyahu/0000018f-339c-d8fb-a1df-bffe7d110000</guid></item><item><title>亲巴勒斯坦学生抗议者与西北大学达成协议以遏制抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-student-protesters-reach-deal-with-university-to-curb-protest-activity/0000018f-33a5-d8d8-a1ff-37f7b5a90000</link><description>与西北大学达成的协议将成立一个新的大学投资和其他承诺咨询委员会，让抗议活动持续到 6 月 1 日，但除了用于援助物资的帐篷外，禁止使用所有帐篷</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-student-protesters-reach-deal-with-university-to-curb-protest-activity/0000018f-33a5-d8d8-a1ff-37f7b5a90000</guid></item><item><title>报告：埃及停火提案中未包含以色列留在加沙的承诺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/report-israeli-commitment-to-stay-out-of-gaza-not-included-in-egypts-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-33c9-d8fb-a1df-bfef92500000</link><description>该提案详细说明，在协议第一阶段将释放 33 名人质，以换取以色列国防军从加沙大部分地区全面撤退并释放巴勒斯坦囚犯。加沙重建计划将在最后阶段实施</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/report-israeli-commitment-to-stay-out-of-gaza-not-included-in-egypts-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-33c9-d8fb-a1df-bfef92500000</guid></item><item><title>艾森科特抨击本-格维尔、斯莫特里奇：我不会加入一个根据政治议程做出决定的政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/eisenkot-blasts-ben-gvir-smotrich-i-wont-be-in-a-govt-that-bases-decisions-on-politics/0000018f-3386-d9c3-abcf-7bf774900000</link><description>这位战时内阁成员指责本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇勒索总理并危害国家安全。斯莫特里奇回答说：“这不是敲诈勒索，而是敲诈勒索。”这是数百万以色列人的合法意见</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/eisenkot-blasts-ben-gvir-smotrich-i-wont-be-in-a-govt-that-bases-decisions-on-politics/0000018f-3386-d9c3-abcf-7bf774900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者不满足于驱逐巴勒斯坦牧羊人，他们还偷走他们的羊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-settlers-arent-content-with-expelling-palestinians-they-also-steal-their-sheep/0000018f-2e83-d8c4-afef-2fff95bc0000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，有关以色列定居者偷窃约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人牛群的报道不断增加。在一起案件中，盗窃发生在身穿制服的男子拘留并殴打牧羊人之后</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:18:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-settlers-arent-content-with-expelling-palestinians-they-also-steal-their-sheep/0000018f-2e83-d8c4-afef-2fff95bc0000</guid></item><item><title>谷歌员工因抗议与以色列签订的合同而被解雇，并向劳工监管机构提出投诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/google-workers-fired-for-protesting-israel-contract-file-complaint-with-labor-regulator/0000018f-3350-d8fb-a1df-bf76f0050000</link><description>数十名在谷歌办公室参加员工静坐后被解雇的谷歌员工向劳工监管机构提出投诉，称他们被“不公平解雇”，以试图夺回工作岗位</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 09:55:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/google-workers-fired-for-protesting-israel-contract-file-complaint-with-labor-regulator/0000018f-3350-d8fb-a1df-bf76f0050000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太作家保罗·奥斯特去世，享年 77 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/jewish-american-author-paul-auster-dies-aged-77/0000018f-3359-d215-afdf-7779b7430000</link><description>奥斯特的作品包括广受好评的小说，如《孤独的发明》、《机遇的音乐》和《4 3 2 1》。他在生命的最后几年一直在与癌症作斗争</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 09:31:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/jewish-american-author-paul-auster-dies-aged-77/0000018f-3359-d215-afdf-7779b7430000</guid></item><item><title>驱逐内塔尼亚胡会解决以色列的一切吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/will-ousting-netanyahu-solve-everything-for-israel/0000018f-3024-d8fb-a1df-bd667f600000</link><description>以色列政府国内外的反对者都坚信内塔尼亚胡是一切问题的根源，从破坏民主到10月7日事件和加沙事件，除掉他将是解决以色列困境的灵丹妙药。讽刺的是，这种说法给了他太多的信任</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 09:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/will-ousting-netanyahu-solve-everything-for-israel/0000018f-3024-d8fb-a1df-bd667f600000</guid></item></channel></rss>